{
  "stem": "15577.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The transportation at that time was a very heavy one and very, very taboo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a-- a distance of maybe 50 miles or 70 miles, something like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was a voyage of a full day, because nothing was working at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went by car, by train, by-- by-- by tracks, by whatever you could.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we arrived in this Erlangen, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and there was a-- a management building of the university.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went in, and I said, what-- what about the opening?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they said, we think we will be open-- opening in two or three months.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And today, we begin the inscription.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who wants and who can, we'll inscribe, if we open.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if the people will be accepted, so we will let know the people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So what shall I do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Fill-- I got such a packet of papers, and I was told to fill it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, I saw every corner, it was a very big room, were standing all the people and filling out these papers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw these papers, and the whole one page or two pages were personal datas.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the others were, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yeah, only questions about what you did during the Nazi time, which party you belong to, and which youth organization you belong to.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what political activities you do, because they wanted to find out who was a Nazi, because those wouldn't be accepted to-- to go to university.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was very, very, very detailed questions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't know how to solve it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I filled out this personal data.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Took two minutes, three minutes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I crossed very page and wrote-- through the cross-- I wrote, 'Jew.' [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was my answer on this.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
